https://desertstarconstruction.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Scottsdale, Arizona, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Desert Star Construction is a well-established company in the local industry and specializes in custom home design and construction services. With a narrative-rich home page consisting of high-quality images and an interesting company news section, the website has great usability and invites visitors to explore its pages. The addition of sleek design elements creates a sophisticated and clean look.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website's home page greets visitors with an impactful page layout. Users can also watch an informative video that showcases the company's building processes, team work, and past projects.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE reports a large number of contrast errors on the site. There are also not enough CTA buttons to entice user engagement, and the "Contact" button in the top-right corner is easy to miss.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-desert-star-construction-desktop-3840x13165-20240614.webp"
