width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website has a polished look that effectively depicts the company's ethos of impeccable craftmanship with crisp images that load fast despite its high resolution. While Google's PageSpeed Insights test gives the site a score of 92/100 in the performance category, site navigation is less intuitive than many competitor sites with no sticky top menu bar.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-desert-star-construction-mobile-824x15743-20240614.webp"
