</span>
<span>Edmonton, Alberta, Canada</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Chandos Construction is a Canada-based, 100% employee-owned company that offers a wide variety of commercial construction services. The website features an engaging hero image slideshow depicting construction workers on site, alongside large headings with links to various site pages, which encourages increased user engagement.</p><p>The use of a bright color scheme accentuates the site's dynamic and professional look, while its selection of high-resolution images reflects ideas of quality and precision.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
