</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site's home page primarily advertises the company's past projects, with additional page links to its services, sustainability, and blog posts available in the top menu bar. The legible typography enhances the overall user experience. WAVE also picked up only a few contrast errors.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
