src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website is missing a dedicated client reviews and/or testimonials section, which would aid in credibility, albeit the company is a B-certified corporation. The CTA buttons could also be made more prominent to optimize user engagement.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-chandos-construction-3840x9744-20240611.webp"
data-type="desktop"
