class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website performs well and its performance score of 95/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test is well-deserved. Users can easily navigate the website with both a top menu bar and a hamburger menu, as well as content-rich pages showcasing the company's work and team. However, pertinent information like the company's hours of operation and location coverage could be added to the home page for additional prominence.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
